org.stellar.sdk

Class StrKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stellar.sdk.StrKey

  • public class StrKey
extends java.lang.Object
    StrKey is a helper class that allows encoding and decoding Stellar keys to/from strings, i.e. between their binary and string (i.e. "GABCD...", etc.) representations.
